						<div class="postbody">I have thought about text entry for text adventure type games, and best I have come up with is a bar that can switch between keywords/items/keyboard and also an on screen cursor that can select any on screen word.  That way you could do things like show room items and click on one of those words.  Should work well for programming where you would have labels/variables to select.  
<br />
<br />The other option is to make a PS/2-&gt;NES adapter with a PIC chip.</div>

